      "id": "PopularPost324693",
      "post_content": "Great card for all the reasons mentioned here, but this isn't an automatic 4-of. That's because the card doesn't have very good synergy **with itself**. If you end up with 2 copies in your hand, then one of the copies is dead.  \n  \nWith that situation in mind, I'd say you should only have 1\u20133 copies (probably 2) unless say you have some other effect like [Wild Guess](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Guess) or [Faithless Looting](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faithless Looting) that can filter your hand.",
      "posted_by": "james2c19v",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost324693\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Great card for all the reasons mentioned here, but this isn't an automatic 4-of. That's because the card doesn't have very good synergy <b>with itself</b>. If you end up with 2 copies in your hand, then one of the copies is dead.<br/><br/>With that situation in mind, I'd say you should only have 1\u20133 copies (probably 2) unless say you have some other effect like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wild Guess\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Guess\">Wild Guess</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Faithless Looting\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faithless Looting\">Faithless Looting</a> that can filter your hand.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '324693'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy24478\">james2c19v</span>\r\n                                (6/29/2013 12:56:45 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl